Sample Contracts



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
AMERICAN HONDA FINANCE CORPORATION, as Seller, and AMERICAN HONDA RECEIVABLES
LLC, as Purchaser RECEIVABLES PURCHASE AGREEMENT Dated May 20, 2015
(May 20th, 2015)
This Receivables Purchase Agreement, dated May 20, 2015, is between American Honda Finance Corporation, a California corporation, as seller, and American Honda Receivables LLC, a Delaware limited liability company, as purchaser.



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
HONDA AUTO RECEIVABLES 2015-2 OWNER TRUST, as Issuer, AMERICAN HONDA
RECEIVABLES LLC, as Seller, and AMERICAN HONDA FINANCE CORPORATION, as Servicer
and Sponsor SALE AND SERVICING AGREEMENT Dated May 20, 2015
(May 20th, 2015)
This Sale and Servicing Agreement, dated May 20, 2015, is among American Honda Receivables LLC, a Delaware limited liability company ("AHR" or, in its capacity as Seller, the "Seller"), American Honda Finance Corporation, a California corporation ("AHFC" or, in its capacity as Servicer, the "Servicer"), and Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust, a Delaware statutory trust, as Issuer (the "Issuer").



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
HONDA AUTO RECEIVABLES 2015-2 OWNER TRUST, as Issuer, AMERICAN HONDA FINANCE
CORPORATION, as Sponsor and Administrator, AMERICAN HONDA RECEIVABLES LLC, as
Depositor, and Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as Indenture Trustee
ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT Dated May 20, 2015
(May 20th, 2015)
This Administration Agreement, dated May 20, 2015 (this "Agreement"), is among Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust, as issuer (the "Issuer"), American Honda Finance Corporation ("AHFC"), as sponsor (in such capacity, the "Sponsor") and administrator (in such capacity, the "Administrator"), American Honda Receivables LLC ("AHR"), as depositor (in such capacity, the "Depositor"), and Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as indenture trustee (the "Indenture Trustee").



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
HONDA AUTO RECEIVABLES 2015-2 OWNER TRUST, as Issuer, and Deutsche Bank Trust
Company Americas, as Indenture Trustee INDENTURE Dated May 20, 2015 CROSS
REFERENCE TABLE*
(May 20th, 2015)
This Indenture, dated May 20, 2015, is between Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust, a Delaware statutory trust (the "Issuer"), and Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as indenture trustee (the "Indenture Trustee").



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
As Depositor, MUFG Union Bank, N.A., as Owner Trustee and U.S. BANK TRUST
NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, as Delaware Trustee AMENDED AND RESTATED TRUST AGREEMENT
Dated May 20, 2015
(May 20th, 2015)
This Amended and Restated Trust Agreement, dated May 20, 2015 is among American Honda Receivables LLC, a Delaware limited liability company, as depositor (the "Depositor"), MUFG Union Bank, N.A., as owner trustee (the "Owner Trustee"), and U.S. Bank Trust National Association, as Delaware trustee (the "Delaware Trustee");



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
AMERICAN HONDA RECEIVABLES LLC, as Seller, HONDA AUTO RECEIVABLES 2015-2 OWNER
TRUST, as Initial Secured Party, AMERICAN HONDA FINANCE CORPORATION, as
Servicer, and DEUTSCHE BANK TRUST COMPANY AMERICAS, as Indenture Trustee, as
Assignee-Secured Party and as Securities Intermediary CONTROL AGREEMENT
(May 20th, 2015)
This Control Agreement, dated May 20, 2015 (this "Agreement"), is among American Honda Receivables LLC (the "Seller"), Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust (the "Initial Secured Party"), American Honda Finance Corporation (the "Servicer"), Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as indenture trustee, as assignee secured party (the "Assignee-Secured Party"), and as securities intermediary (the "Securities Intermediary").



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
HONDA AUTO RECEIVABLES 2015-2 OWNER TRUST, as Issuer, AMERICAN HONDA FINANCE
CORPORATION, as Sponsor and Administrator, AMERICAN HONDA RECEIVABLES LLC, as
Depositor, and Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as Indenture Trustee
ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT Dated May 20, 2015
(May 15th, 2015)
This Administration Agreement, dated May 20, 2015 (this "Agreement"), is among Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust, as issuer (the "Issuer"), American Honda Finance Corporation ("AHFC"), as sponsor (in such capacity, the "Sponsor") and administrator (in such capacity, the "Administrator"), American Honda Receivables LLC ("AHR"), as depositor (in such capacity, the "Depositor"), and Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as indenture trustee (the "Indenture Trustee").



Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust –
As Depositor, MUFG Union Bank, N.A., as Owner Trustee and U.S. BANK TRUST
NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, as Delaware Trustee AMENDED AND RESTATED TRUST AGREEMENT
Dated May 20, 2015
(May 15th, 2015)
This Amended and Restated Trust Agreement, dated May 20, 2015 is among American Honda Receivables LLC, a Delaware limited liability company, as depositor (the "Depositor"), MUFG Union Bank, N.A., as owner trustee (the "Owner Trustee"), and U.S. Bank Trust National Association, as Delaware trustee (the "Delaware Trustee");



