(May 15th, 2015)
This Control Agreement, dated May 20, 2015 (this "Agreement"), is among American Honda Receivables LLC (the "Seller"), Honda Auto Receivables 2015-2 Owner Trust (the "Initial Secured Party"), American Honda Finance Corporation (the "Servicer"), Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas, as indenture trustee, as assignee secured party (the "Assignee-Secured Party"), and as securities intermediary (the "Securities Intermediary").



